query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_properties,
  COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN id IN (SELECT DISTINCT property_id FROM property_images) THEN id END) as properties_with_images,
  COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN id NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT property_id FROM property_images) THEN id END) as properties_without_images,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM property_images) as total_images,
  (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT property_id) FROM property_images) as unique_properties_with_images
FROM properties WHERE source = 'zillow';
